<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="4f43587a-e149-44cc-bc9c-ab2017780dd7"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16843-doppelganger" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16843-tooltip">Doppelganger</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="a426ef29-f4c0-4b36-9224-0d23aa0c5f23">Medium monstrosity (shapechanger), neutral</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="a8321099-17ad-4933-a6e9-367d235d39be"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="60e6b00a-147b-46ab-95fc-50cb497b8e53">Armo</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2848c5ea-be5c-4701-95c0-403e2c916d11">r Class</span>&nbsp;14</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="5f17f493-846d-4dfc-99d7-e8b1b2d54cce"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="566738ba-3300-4504-b93b-636eb6a35467">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;52 (8d8 + 16)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="a26b244f-1a28-41e2-966e-9c6b472a91c4"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="23ed1eec-ae3d-4af6-ba68-7c767b23ac22">Sp</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d4e2d9f3-ee77-4463-a1ce-94b403891f2e">eed</span>&nbsp;30 ft.</p>
