<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-stat" data-content-chunk-id="06383b67-5de2-4cd4-b056-c482449a8067">
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-heading" data-content-chunk-id="96ea92b1-f326-4dbf-a79a-8fb8cbc4eb57">WIS</div>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="f9741eae-89d0-40fb-a198-3c6af2eb9bdd"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="111b2303-ac37-4082-8b95-10ac3bba465a">11</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="4a18c3de-eecd-461b-a5e8-ebf0574fb49c">(+0)</span></div>
</div>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-stat" data-content-chunk-id="1d898f6a-7320-449a-81a6-c521ca6df28c">
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-heading" data-content-chunk-id="4b641b8a-1d9d-4588-9e05-5fba02acfeae">CHA</div>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="1e5da608-feb3-44a7-b38a-3e0702982865"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="c48facd0-56ae-4f76-91ec-003e7a8618ca">10</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="07d1b28d-ba5e-4c54-acfc-67d1d252f1a7">(+0)</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="0b173af7-c9a6-4b98-962d-e9210af38eb5"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2dd4c559-0f10-436f-a2b8-9560f87e8553">Skills</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a> +2, <a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Stealth" data-tooltip-href="/skills/5-tooltip">Stealth</a> +4</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="7adb01f8-fa81-49bb-830f-fbea7272f5ec"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="da167234-0913-4f19-a061-507fb177d265">Damage Vulnerabil</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="762e855f-0688-4c15-8d51-af9c71f7f157">ities</span>&nbsp;fire</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="beb9bdec-addf-45a8-a986-c29022757216"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="dc8a3754-01b6-446c-b6e2-b882eed97348">Damage Immunit</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3d5ed1c8-df4d-4b31-91f8-27fba50b54be">ies</span>&nbsp;poison</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="366bc87e-33ef-46c6-a5bb-c6d15dd02c4c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6103a4db-9d89-48d9-a7f4-77dae2a236fd">Condition Immunitie</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7e614a3c-8e4d-4cbb-b62c-29b4f48e541a">s</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="dc23a5b1-c4a7-4ea6-977e-5b9c11e7222a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="81d27673-048d-434a-8fbc-1bf35567e354">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 60 ft., passive Perception 12</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2febf2a2-0837-4e75-9e23-122c0a20606b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="99da87bb-d9a5-4d74-8a71-9b7a0fe4530f">Languages</span>&nbsp;Auran, Terran</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="13ad3102-d206-4541-9be6-840d3fa34157"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7db2d98b-0cb0-45a0-a727-2412ba112b4b">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="94500857-7ea6-4443-a2f2-c9e3710d3896"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1bf1c2aa-9ff3-4811-af38-c984239a1ce4">Death Burst.&nbsp;</span>When the mephit dies, it explodes in a burst of dust. Each creature within 5 feet of it must then succeed on a DC 10 Constitution saving throw or be <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Blinded" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/1-tooltip">blinded</a> for 1 minute. A <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Blinded" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/1-tooltip">blinded</a> creature can repeat the saving throw on each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="c57e91b8-65ea-4b1b-ac15-5ac175d02123"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8a0e387e-d5ef-4062-ba87-df079e610ae5">Innate Spellcasting (1/Day).</span>&nbsp;The mephit can innately cast&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="02817bff-6438-4e40-af67-58d0b29d82f5">sleep</span>, requiring no material components. Its innate spellcasting ability is Charisma.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="b0232bdb-3e97-4147-b4e8-a83c7f13b83b">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="60e8d36d-cba4-464c-9353-dc16ce9a9552"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="bf2f4040-3974-4e5c-9efb-56563162efd6">Claws.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2a7a91eb-e404-437a-82ec-21129362492a">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d905b186-73a2-40d5-8e93-07f3c6977e45">Hit:</span>&nbsp;4 (1d4 + 2) slashing damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="702b99d6-bcf1-4aa2-a804-a21100d080aa"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="352c2cd4-9821-48bc-a4f9-adc93937e8e4">Blinding Breath (Recharge 6).&nbsp;</span>The mephit exhales a 15-foot cone of blinding dust. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity saving throw or be <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Blinded" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/1-tooltip">blinded</a> for 1 minute. A creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>
</div>
    </div>

